An example of electric field gated thermal switch by nanojunction consisting of two gold nanoparticles bridged by a ferrocenyl molecule. 

If this simulation example helps, please cite our paper.
Title:
Thermal Switching in a Ferrocenyl Nanojunction Is Observed in All-Atom Simulations
